<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #9966ff">Certainly, brother! What you are looking at is the fission reactor control console. There is a counterpart console located outside the chamber, but this one is directly hardwired into the control rod manipulator for direct adjustments.</span></p>
<p><br /></p>
<table class="wiki-content-table">
