<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #9966ff">You got it, zippy! The fission reactor is how the site generates power. The control rods control the reactor, either by increasing or decreasing the reaction or power generated. Currently fifteen of twenty are engaged. The more you lift up, the more power. Does that make sense now?</span></p>
