<td>I did the SCRAM thingy and hit the button.</td>
</tr>
</table>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://kaktuskontainer.wdfiles.com/local--files/lurk-work/AIC.png" width="40px" alt="AIC.png" class="image" /></div>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #9966ff">Well slap me around and call me Clippy. I'm sure it was because of an emergency. I'll just call in the MTF and they'll take care of the aftermath.</span></p>
<p><br /></p>
<table class="wiki-content-table">
