<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #9966ff">Too late, trigger! They are mobilizing now. I'm also detecting a few breaches here and there that they will need to respond to first. Apparently cutting the power out suddenly doesn't give enough time for the backups to start up on some chambers.</span></p>
<p><br /></p>
